headline: Jack Henry and Moov to Implement Visa Direct to Enable Fast, Seamless Payments
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today its collaboration with Visa, the world leader in digital payments, to offer Visa Direct through Jack Henry Rapid Transfers™. The addition of Visa Direct, which facilitates the delivery of funds directly to eligible cards, bank accounts, and wallets around the world, is part of Jack Henry's previously announced alliance with Moov to enable community and regional financial institutions to offer robust and comprehensive digital payment services to consumer
